<lyrics>[V1]
 Sui le ngun in a si lo, Keimah sualtlanhnak, Vawlei chawhlawn nih ka
 thlarau a khamh lo, Vailamtahnak thi lawng ka hram fek lung a si, Keimah
 Khamhbawi thih ca'h, a tu ka him cang.

[C1]
   Keimah tlanhnak ngun in a si lo, Sui zongin a si fawn lo, Bawi Jesuh
   thi nih a ka cawk cang, Chim cawk lo dawtnak man sung.

[V2]
 Sui le ngun in a si lo, Keimah sualtlanhnak, Keimah lungchung sualnak
 kha a rit ko cang, Vailamtahnak thi lawng ka hram fek lung a si, Ka
 khamhtu thihnak lawng nih a liam khawh lai.

[C2]
   Keimah tlanhnak ngun in a si lo, Sui zongin a si fawn lo, Bawi Jesuh
   thi nih a ka cawk cang, Chim cawk lo dawtnak man sung.

[V3]
 Sui le ngun in a si lo, Keimah sualtlanhnak, Raithawinak zong nih a
 kan khamh kho fawn lo, Vailamtahnak thi lawng ka hram fek lung a si, Ka
 tihnak Khamhbawi thihnak nih a hloh cang.

[C3]
   Keimah tlanhnak ngun in a si lo, Sui zongin a si fawn lo, Bawi Jesuh
   thi nih a ka cawk cang, Chim cawk lo dawtnak man sung.

[V4]
 Sui le ngun in a si lo, Keimah sual tlanhnak, Khi bang in vancung
 luhnak ka caw kho lo, Vailam tahnak thi lawng ka hram fek lung a si,
 Khamhbawi thihnak in sual tlanhnak ka hmuh cang.

[C4]
   Keimah tlanhnak ngun in a si lo, Sui zongin a si fawn lo, Bawi Jesuh
   thi nih a ka cawk cang, Chim cawk lo dawtnak man sung.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>SUI LE NGUN IN A SI LO CH156</title>
</song>